<p>Roofing has one of the highest customer lifetime values in home services. A single residential roof replacement averages $8,000 to $15,000. Commercial jobs run $25,000 to $100,000 or more. The cost to acquire that customer through SEO is a fraction of what you would spend on paid ads or lead generation services.</p>
