<p>Compare that to HomeAdvisor or Angi leads at $50 to $150 per lead, shared with 3 to 5 other roofers. Or Google Ads at $30 to $80 per click for roofing keywords with no guarantee of conversion.</p>
<p>SEO compounds over time. Every blog post, every review, every optimized page builds on the last. After 6 months of consistent SEO, your cost per lead drops while your lead volume increases. Paid ads stop the moment you stop paying. SEO keeps working.</p>
